5. NOTIFICATION REQUIREMENTS:
   - Foreground service MUST show persistent notification
   - Notification cannot be dismissed by user while service runs
   - Provide clear, user-friendly notification text

6. LOCATION ACCURACY:
   - HIGH_ACCURACY uses GPS (high battery usage)
   - BALANCED_POWER uses network + GPS (moderate battery)
   - LOW_POWER uses network only (low battery)
